casebody.data:
Richard BENEVENTO, Plaintiff-Movant,
v.
Alyssa BENEVENTO, Defendant-Respondent. M-658 September Term 2018
082142 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 8, 2019

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for leave to appeal is denied. It is further ORDERED that the appeal now proceeding in the Superior Court, Appellate Division (A-000602-18) shall be expedited, with the matter proceeding on an accelerated schedule to be established by the Appellate Division Clerk's Office.
